<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .ticket-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    .ticket-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .ticket-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .ticket-header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .ticket-body {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .ticket-info {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .ticket-info p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .ticket-info strong {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .ticket-items {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .ticket-items table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .ticket-items th {
      background: #f1f3f4;
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .ticket-items td {
      padding: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .ticket-total {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #27ae60;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .ticket-footer {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
    }
    .btn-volver {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #3498db;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-volver:hover {
      background: #2980b9;
    }
    .failed-products {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      color: #856404;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="ticket-container">
    <div class="ticket-header">
      <h1>🎫 COMPROBANTE DE COMPRA</h1>
      <p>¡Gracias por tu compra!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="ticket-body">
      <div class="ticket-info">
        <p><strong>📄 Número de ticket:</strong> {{ticket.code}}</p>
        <p><strong>📅 Fecha:</strong> {{formatDate ticket.purchase_datetime}}</p>
        <p><strong>👤 Cliente:</strong> {{ticket.purchaser}}</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="ticket-items">
        <h3>📦 Productos comprados</h3>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Producto</th>
              <th>Cantidad</th>
              <th>Precio unit.</th>
              <th>Subtotal</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {{#each purchasedItems}}
              <tr>
                <td>{{this.product.title}}</td>
                <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
                <td>${{this.product.price}}</td>
                <td>${{multiply this.product.price this.quantity}}</td>
              </tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      
      <div class="ticket-total">
        TOTAL: ${{ticket.amount}}
      </div>
      
      {{#if failedProducts.length}}
        <div class="failed-products">
          <strong>⚠️ Productos no disponibles (sin stock):</strong>
          <ul>
            {{#each failedProducts}}
              <li>{{this.title}} - Código: {{this.code}}</li>
            {{/each}}
          </ul>
          <p>Estos productos no se incluyeron en la compra y permanecen en tu carrito.</p>
        </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    <div class="ticket-footer">
      <p>Este comprobante es válido como constancia de compra.</p>
      <p>Para cualquier consulta, contacta a soporte@ecommerce.com</p>
      <a href="/products" class="btn-volver">🛍️ Seguir comprando</a>
      <a href="/carts/{{cartId}}" class="btn-volver" style="background: #95a5a6;">🛒 Ver carrito</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
